Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.m.message

Integrity measurement component message interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImMessage
    Generic integrity measurement component message base consisting of a message header and a set of integrity measurement attributes.
    ImMessageHeader
    Generic integrity measurement component message header base consisting of general parameters, that describe a message.
    ImMessageHeaderBuilder
    Generic builder base to build an integrity measurement component message header.
